{"tid":501051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"每個年代都會有班女吹捧一條根本唔撚靚既女—袁澧林","createTime":"2017-12-16T12:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:05:06.000Z","uid":32051,"like":44,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64cea560cb48f04e1f22342e991b2c32afafc5e4","tid":501051,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"細個聽到班豬閪同學吹捧舒琪<br />\n搞到細細個一直懷疑自己審美<br />\n見到舒琪果對分開到成件弱智村姑咁既閪眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/200603_f352d8408057c851d5f2fb989913fe66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F200603_f352d8408057c851d5f2fb989913fe66.jpg&h=354a2934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再加佢薄而大加反既朱脣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/200616_40ed561dac85667bbba8201af59862c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F200616_40ed561dac85667bbba8201af59862c7.jpg&h=f0981638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你知唔知我細個幾想大聲講，舒琪好撚樣衰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到依家又有班女吹捧一件文青女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/200903_82a614b2d1f9651ac00819f1385fbe05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F200903_82a614b2d1f9651ac00819f1385fbe05.jpg&h=c24fee26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普通成咁叫女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得成日有人話係女都女神 有閪都叫女神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/200924_4a95363df2ccf2e1bf7c75dded38611d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F200924_4a95363df2ccf2e1bf7c75dded38611d.jpg&h=3f10dd92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪眼袋改個叫法做臥蠶就當左靚？<br />\n係咪五爪金龍刺繡柒鼻就叫有特色？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/202200_96dc8fdc8f8171e8fba7039e0ce31f10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F202200_96dc8fdc8f8171e8fba7039e0ce31f10.jpg&h=0758839b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解每個年代都有班女刻意吹捧一班唔撚靚既女做女神？<br />\n係咪因為吹捧一個唔靚既女做女神，可以將你地同女神既距離拉近？<br />\n係咪想後代對美產生歧異？<br />\n你知唔知你地咁做好大影響？<br />\n知唔知？<br />\n你地為左一己私利，隨時搞到影響生態平衡，你班臭閪唔好再追捧班怪樣女<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/16/202412_0630436da58f5779bc089bfcb28a502d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2F202412_0630436da58f5779bc089bfcb28a502d.jpg&h=9397de0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPost定俾你班人quote<br />\n利申其中一位 好未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實真心唔係故意反<br />\nModel界不嬲都有班靠怪樣突圍<br />\n但唔好明明奇葩咁既樣 硬係要人覺得佢大眾覺得靚 好唔好？"},{"pid":"f5d42d0f6fd38a6e7cdfd2e90593a936437b3f6e","tid":501051,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"你講左你係邊個我先認真答你"},{"pid":"05e9cba3cc0cd102eb9b735d771cb555cfee196a","tid":501051,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講左你係邊個我先認真答你</blockquote><br />\n毒撚辨識度低<br />\n講黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7faf32e79736ce668c452e5ed3ad7da5ced0f66c","tid":501051,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f324aec7ea852415f3e691f583d7f34f96bf0a3","tid":501051,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:02:17.000Z","msg":"見到個眼袋, 不了"},{"pid":"6aa93b5f7cc273f8b35f94350442634a32cba268","tid":501051,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:05:59.000Z","msg":"袁澧林你唔要我要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n晚晚同佢瘋狂唱吻下去 便確定我共你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba66adbb370cbc339efb915955da583d51add9b","tid":501051,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"我，初代大鼻𡃁模追擊手，今日終於搵到有知音"}]}